briefdescription.para: Manipulator to cause the next PcpLayerStackIdentifier written to the ostream to write the base name of its layers, rather than the full identifier.
Manipulator to cause the next PcpLayerStackIdentifier written to the ostream to write the real path of its layers, rather than the identifier.
Manipulator to cause the next PcpLayerStackIdentifier written to the ostream to write the identifier of its layers.

detaileddescription.para: This is the default state; this manipulator is only to nullify one of the above manipulators.
